      "id": 746,
      "from_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "to_id": "cec50b17:23",
      "content": "Move PLAN.md from the project root to `.synapse/PLAN.md` and update the dashboard to read it from there.\n\n**Steps:**\n\n1. In `src/dashboard.ts`, change line:\n   ```typescript\n   const PLAN_PATH = join(process.cwd(), 'PLAN.md');\n   ```\n   to:\n   ```typescript\n   const PLAN_PATH = join(process.cwd(), '.synapse', 'PLAN.md');\n   ```\n\n2. Copy the current `PLAN.md` content to `.synapse/PLAN.md` (use the Read tool on `PLAN.md` then Write to `.synapse/PLAN.md`).\n\n3. Remove `PLAN.md` from git tracking: `git rm PLAN.md`\n\n4. Run `npm run build` to rebuild dist/.\n\n5. Commit: `Move PLAN.md to .synapse/PLAN.md; update dashboard path`\n\nReport DONE to cec50b17:0.",
